<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/46669828-dinethi-jayasinghe">Dinethi Jayasinghe</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">According to the book,it is not directly said that Monte was a part of the operation doomsday, but as we read we find that Monte was one of Willard St<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">According to the book,it is not directly said that Monte was a part of the operation doomsday, but as we read we find that Monte was one of Willard Stone's business partners and Janus had used him to separate Susan and Robert and at the end Monte was also taken with the aliens.<br />So that we can assume Monte also had played a significant role in the conspiracy.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
