        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1659400081" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3322294862227055237">As much as I like Sidney Sheldon&apos;s books, this didn&apos;t live up to expectation. Out of everything I&apos;ve read this is the only book that didn&apos;t manage to give me goosebumps. I think this government conspiracy shit is just not for him.</span>
  <span id="freeText3322294862227055237" style="display:none">As much as I like Sidney Sheldon's books, this didn't live up to expectation. Out of everything I've read this is the only book that didn't manage to give me goosebumps. I think this government conspiracy shit is just not for him.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3322294862227055237" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


